#: experiment.py
msgid "Quality"
msgstr "Qualité"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Cost saving"
msgstr "Économie de coût"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Community benefit"
msgstr "Bénéfice pour la communauté"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Comfort"
msgstr "Confort"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Environmental impact"
msgstr "Impact environnemental"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Long-term value"
msgstr "Valeur à long terme"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Fit with local needs"
msgstr "Adaptation aux besoins locaux"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Reliability"
msgstr "Fiabilité"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Flexibility"
msgstr "Flexibilité"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Family preference"
msgstr "Préférence familiale"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Time saving"
msgstr "Gain de temps"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Safety"
msgstr "Sécurité"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Social approval"
msgstr "Approbation sociale"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Future opportunity"
msgstr "Opportunité future"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Low effort required"
msgstr "Faible effort requis"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Instructions"
msgstr "Instructions"

#: experiment.py
msgid ""
"On each trial you will see two options side by side. Each option has several"
" features."
msgstr ""
"À chaque essai, vous verrez deux options côte à côte. Chaque option comporte"
" plusieurs caractéristiques."

#: experiment.py
msgid ""
"Every feature has a value from 0 to 100 and a validity from 0 to 1. Higher "
"validity means the feature is a more reliable cue."
msgstr ""
"Chaque caractéristique a une valeur de 0 à 100 et une validité de 0 à 1. Une"
" validité plus élevée signifie que la caractéristique est un indice plus "
"fiable."

#: experiment.py
msgid ""
"Please compare the two options carefully and choose the option you would "
"prefer."
msgstr ""
"Veuillez comparer attentivement les deux options et choisir celle que vous "
"préféreriez."

#: experiment.py
msgid ""
"There are no right or wrong answers. We are interested in your decision."
msgstr ""
"Il n’y a pas de bonnes ou de mauvaises réponses. Votre décision nous "
"intéresse."

#: experiment.py
msgid "Welcome"
msgstr "Bienvenue"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Thank you for taking part in this decision-making study."
msgstr "Merci de participer à cette étude sur la prise de décision."

#: experiment.py
msgid "You will make a short series of choices between two described options."
msgstr "Vous ferez une courte série de choix entre deux options décrites."

#: experiment.py
msgid "Feature"
msgstr "Caractéristique"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Value"
msgstr "Valeur"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Validity"
msgstr "Validité"

#: experiment.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Option {LETTER}"
msgstr "Option {LETTER}"

#: experiment.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Trial {NUMBER}"
msgstr "Essai {NUMBER}"

#: experiment.py
msgid ""
"Review the feature values and validities, then choose the option you would "
"prefer."
msgstr ""
"Examinez les valeurs et les validités des caractéristiques, puis choisissez "
"l’option que vous préféreriez."

#: experiment.py
msgid ""
"Full instructions: values range from 0 to 100, validities range from 0 to 1,"
" and higher validity means a more reliable cue."
msgstr ""
"Instructions complètes : les valeurs vont de 0 à 100, les validités vont de "
"0 à 1, et une validité plus élevée signifie un indice plus fiable."

#: experiment.py
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Choose Option {LETTER}"
msgstr "Choisir l’option {LETTER}"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Thank you"
msgstr "Merci"

#: experiment.py
msgid "Thank you for completing the decision-making study."
msgstr "Merci d’avoir terminé l’étude sur la prise de décision."
